item.description:
Charges require the infomation below in order to successfully complete a charge.

```json
{
	"id_currency": "523a25953b8e77910e8b456c",
    // String, ID currency corresponding to MXN
    "transaction": "ff9d8b219b468317bc63ca29196e0fb4701fbbfc",
    // String, ID of transaction
    "internal_reference": "ff9d8b219b468317bc63ca29196e0fb4701fbbfc",
    // String, internal reference
    "reference": "20190814/0GZXXG81",
    // String, transaction reference
    "description": "Descripcion de Cargo",
    // String, description of charge
    "amount": 50
    // Float, charge amount
}
```
